of Disney share prices, fueled by far more than takeover rumors.
   Disney recently reported its second-quarter profit rose 24
percent, its summer movies have turned in better-than-expected
performances and attendance has been so strong at its new studios
theme park that Disney plans to double the size of the Orlando,
Fla., attraction.
   Disney disclosed this week that it plans a new sea-oriented
theme park next to the Queen Mary and Spruce Goose attractions in
Long Beach.
